title: Ep. 70: 'Stranger Things,' 'Mr. Robot,' and 'You're the Worst' Re-up
description:
Chris Ryan and Andy Greenwald discuss Season 2 of 'Stranger Things,' and whether we'll get Barb back. Then, they talk about 'Mr. Robot' and the premiere of the third season of 'You're the Worst.'
